---
---

<html lang="it">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Sibillini Europa Gallery Widget</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
        background: #f4f0e8;
        color: #1f2937;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-block-size: 100vh;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.45), transparent 35%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #f8f5ef 0%, #f0ece3 100%);
      }

      main {
        max-inline-size: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 4rem 1.5rem 6rem;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      }

      p {
        max-inline-size: 66ch;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      section + section {
        margin-block-start: 3rem;
      }
    </style>
    <script>
      window.GALLERY_WIDGET_BASE_URL = "/";
    </script>
    <script type="module">
      import "../widget/widget.js";
    </script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>Standalone gallery widget</h1>
      <p>
        Questa pagina Astro serve solo per verificare localmente il widget embeddabile.
        In produzione WordPress usera il bundle statico buildato da Vite.
      </p>

      <section>
        <h2>Estate 2025</h2>
        <div class="gallery-widget" data-gallery="estate-2025"></div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Evento X</h2>
        <div class="gallery-widget" data-gallery="evento-x"></div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
